k\": 0.34260107369813353, \"text\": \"Washington\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Washington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sea otters are not normally a migratory species, which is why a local population has not reestablished itself.\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The alliance says the sighting is a hopeful sign.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2025Sinclair, Inc.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": []}]}"